<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id74a38f70-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s153506"><num value="153506">§ 153506.</num><heading> Exclusive right to name</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The corporation has the exclusive right to use and to allow others to use the name “National Tropical Botanical Garden”.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id74a38f71-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(<ref href="/us/pl/105/225">Pub. L. 105–225</ref>, <date date="1998-08-12">Aug. 12, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/1426">112 Stat. 1426</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
